model.card

Class Deck

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.card.Deck

  • public class Deck
extends java.lang.Object
    Deck class describes an object of a deck of shuffled cards used for the game of poker.

    The hand is represented by a Stack.

    9/26/2016
    Version:
